---
---
<div class="about-terminal">
  <div class="terminal-bar">
    <span class="terminal-dots">
      <span class="dot-purple"></span>
      <span class="dot-yellow"></span>
      <span class="dot-grey"></span>
    </span>
    <span class="terminal-title">about.exe</span>
    <span class="terminal-close">&times;</span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-body">
    <div class="cmd"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> whoami</div>
    <div class="output">Lyla Huang — Strategist turned builder</div>

    <div class="cmd"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> run career.log</div>
    <div class="log-entries">
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2015]</span><span class="log-label">SIGNAL_START</span><span class="log-body">Graduated NUS. Started writing ads.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2015–17]</span><span class="log-label">HAVAS_SG</span><span class="log-body">Grew client IG <span class="hl">4000%</span>. First awards.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2018–21]</span><span class="log-label">BLKJ_SENIOR</span><span class="log-body">Senior Writer. Led <span class="hl">8 creatives</span>. Award-winning.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2021–22]</span><span class="log-label">GOOGLE_APAC</span><span class="log-body"><span class="hl">133 SMEs</span> across APAC. Content at scale.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2022–24]</span><span class="log-label">FREELANCE</span><span class="log-body"><span class="hl">20+ clients</span>. Strategy, copy, brand.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2024]</span><span class="log-label">PIVOT</span><span class="log-body">Barcelona. Master's in <span class="hl">HAI</span>.</span></div>
      <div class="log-row"><span class="log-date">[2025–26]</span><span class="log-label">BUILD_MODE</span><span class="log-body">Code. Products. AI. <span class="dim">// current</span></span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="cmd"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> ls /archive/</div>
    <div class="archive-list">
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">scoot-savage/</span><span class="note">4× Award Winner</span></div>
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">onward/</span><span class="note">National TVC</span></div>
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">passion-stories/</span><span class="note">Brand Film Series</span></div>
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">fairprice-pun/</span><span class="note">Gold · Markies 2017</span></div>
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">hipsters/</span><span class="note">Brand Film</span></div>
      <div class="archive-row"><span class="dir">inflight/</span><span class="note">Video Series</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="cmd"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> cat awards.txt</div>
    <div class="awards-output">
      <div>Rising Star · Creative Circles '18</div>
      <div>Gold · Markies '17</div>
      <div>2S + 3B · Creative Circles '18</div>
      <div>Grand Prize · IG Cannes '16</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cmd"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> echo "message"</div>
    <div class="pullquote-output">
      "I spent a decade learning to turn noise into signal for brands.<br>
      Now I design the signal itself."
    </div>

    <span class="cursor-blink">█</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about-terminal {
    background: var(--dark);
    margin: 0 -2.5rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .terminal-bar {
    background: var(--dark-light);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .terminal-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .terminal-dots span {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot-purple { background: var(--purple); }
  .dot-yellow { background: var(--yellow); }
  .dot-grey { background: #666; }

  .terminal-title {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .terminal-close {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: #666;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem 3rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .cmd {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--yellow);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cmd:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--yellow);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .output {
    color: #ccc;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .log-entries {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .log-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .log-date {
    color: #888;
    min-width: 6ch;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .log-label {
    color: var(--purple);
    font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 12ch;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .log-body {
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .hl {
    color: var(--yellow);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .dim {
    color: #666;
  }

  .archive-list {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .archive-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .dir {
    color: var(--purple);
    min-width: 18ch;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .note {
    color: #888;
  }

  .awards-output {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .pullquote-output {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--yellow);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cursor-blink {
    color: var(--yellow);
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-terminal {
      margin: 0 -1.5rem;
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .log-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .archive-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
